Sainsbury's ya shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya.
Sainsbury's yana karɓar jiragen ruwa, super drug da Debenhams, tare da sassan kayan kwalliya na salon kantin sayar da kayayyaki tare da ƙwararrun mataimaka.
A wani bangare na wani babban ci gaba a kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya mai darajar fam biliyan 2.8, wanda ke ci gaba da ci gaba yayin da ake dawo da kayan kwalliya da kayan gida, waɗannan manyan sassan kayan kwalliyar za su kasance a cikin shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar, da kuma ƙarin shaguna a cikin shekara mai zuwa idan sun yi nasara.
Manyan kantuna suna saka hannun jari a cikin kayan kwalliya saboda suna son cike ɗakunan ajiya waɗanda aka keɓe don TV, microwaves da sauran kayan gida.
Sainsbury's ya ce za su kara girman kayan kwalliyarta zuwa kayayyaki 3,000, wadanda suka hada da Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees, waɗanda suka riga sun zama na yanzu, za su sami ƙarin sarari tare da yankuna masu alama, kamar yadda a cikin shagunan jirgin ruwa.
Har ila yau, babban kanti ya sake sake fasalin kayan kwalliyarsa, don haka yawancin kayayyakin suna da abokantaka da vegan, wanda ke ƙara buƙatar matasa masu amfani.
Mai sayar da turare The Fragrance Shop zai gwada cinikayya a shagunan Sainsbury's guda biyu, tare da buɗewa na farko a Croydon, a kudancin London a makon da ya gabata da kuma na biyu a Selly Oak, Birmingham, wanda zai buɗe a ƙarshen wannan shekarar.
Siyayya ta yanar gizo da ƙananan kayan abinci na yau da kullun da ƙananan shaguna suna nufin cewa manyan kantuna dole ne suyi ƙoƙari don sa mutane su zo su saya.
Mike Coupe, manajan Sainsbury's, ya ce wuraren sayar da kayayyaki za su zama kamar manyan kantuna, saboda sarkar kantin sayar da kayayyaki na kokarin yin gasa da masu sayar da kayayyaki masu yawa da ba abinci ba Aldi da Lidl.
ainsbury's ya buɗe shagunan Argos da ɗaruruwan shagunan bayan gida da kuma wasu shagunan Habitats tun lokacin da babban kanti ya sayi duka sarkar shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na sayar da kayan kwalliya da kantin magani ya kasa.
A farkon shekarun 2000, Sainsbury's ya gwada haɗin gwiwa tare da jiragen ruwa, amma haɗin gwiwar ya ƙare da sauri bayan rikici game da rabon kuɗin da kantin magani da manyan kantuna ke samu.
