Trump ya yi rangadin zaben a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia, da yamma.
Wannan shi ne karon farko na ziyarar Trump na mako guda, inda zai tsaya a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake kuri'un amincewa sun yi yawa a zabensa a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, Trump ya yi watsi da tsoratar da za a yi a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki idan aka gudanar da zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi zaben Trump a jihar West Virginia a yau da yamma kuma ta yaya za ka iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron zaben Trump na West Virginia a daren yau, Samhain, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, karfe 7 na yamma ET.
Kuna iya kallon taron zaben Trump na West Virginia ta hanyar layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump ya ambaci gabatarwar da aka yi a wannan makon ga wanda aka zaba a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka dakatar da zabensa na mako guda saboda zargin cin zarafin tsohuwar sanata yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma burin farko shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasarar tsayawa takara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban Amurka Trump ya ce, taron biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, zai taimaka wajen karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya bayansu, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba, ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya shi a gidan wasan kwaikwayo na Westbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron zauren zai iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da yamma kuma za a ba da rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata guda da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke faduwa a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don taimaka masa ya sami rinjaye a cikin kuri'un", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
