An ci gaba da shan kaye a hannun Rangers ta hanyar burin Dolly Menga wanda ya rage wa Steven Gerrard 1-0.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta yi kokarin tabbatar da wasanta na farko tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da ta yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta samu rashin nasara a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 da Gerrard ya yi a matsayin kocin, inda ta rage maki takwas a ragar kungiyar ta Ladbrokes, Hearts.
Menga ya zira kwallo minti bakwai kafin rabin lokaci kuma tawagar Rangers ta rasa wahayi kuma ba ta iya ci gaba ba.
Yayin da Rangers ke sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku, a bayan Hiberian ta hanyar bambanci a cikin burin.
Kuma akwai yiwuwar wasu matsaloli na kara tasowa a Rangers bayan da aka yi wa mai tsaron gida Calum Spence jinya saboda ciwon kai, sakamakon wani abu da aka yi da alama an harbe shi a ƙarshen wasan.
