Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi zai dace da bangaren tattalin arzikin kasar da kuma shirin da ake yi na yiwa kasar aiki.
Canja zuwa mako na kwana hudu yana goyon bayan Kungiyar Kungiyar Kwadago, a matsayin wata hanya ta bawa ma'aikata fa'idodin tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa ana sa ran sanar da wani nazari kan manufofin a karshen shekara.
Ba za a iya yin shi ba cikin dare, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako shine burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyarsa na daidaita tattalin arziki da kuma goyon bayan ma'aikata da kuma tsarin dabarun masana'antu.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta amince da wannan ra'ayi ba, Green ta riga ta yi magana a kan yakin neman zaben 2017 don mako hudu.
Amma wannan burin ba shi da goyon baya a jam'iyyar Labour.
