China, kamar yadda Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register, yanzu tana karawa da shi wani jirgin ruwa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridunmu.
