Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican da ke bayan dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh ke tsayawa a baya da baya don kare wasu zarge-zarge na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a fuskanci mummunan sakamako a zaben, musamman daga mata.
Motsin zuciyar da ke tattare da batun ya kasance mai girma, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun ce suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya kawar da irin wannan abu ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, wanda ya yi magana da The Hill don wani labarin da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Reeher ya ce Sanata Jeff Flake (R  Arizona) ya matsa lamba a karshe don samun binciken FBI kawai don kawo masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba. Ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kasa ga kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, idan za a iya gaskanta jaridar Washington D.C.
Masu zanga-zangar ranar Juma'a sun yi ihu yayin da suke tafiya a cikin majalisar dattijai, suna cewa "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh, duk da bayanin da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ya yi, a cewar wani rahoto.
"Democratic himma da kuma dalili zai zama matsananci",Stu Rothenberg, wani ba jam'iyyar siyasa Analyst, ya gaya wa News site.
Mutane sun ce ya riga ya yi girma; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a, a cikin birane da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda - ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa - sau da yawa ba sa zaɓe.
Ko da kafin shaidar jama'a ta Ford, inda ta ba da cikakken bayanin cin zarafin jima'i ga dan takarar Kotun Koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa zai iya komawa baya idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan rikice-rikice ne ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun mai jefa kuri'a ko mai jefa kuri'a na karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai zama alkali ba, amma kuma batun yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da su", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimaka wa 'yan Democrat su samu zabe, ga wata tashar talabijin.
Amma jama'ar Amurka sun nuna rashin jituwa game da abin da za su yi imani da shi daga maganganun Ford da Kavanaugh, kodayake akwai karkata ga gaskatawa da na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun yi imani da cewa Ford ya yi magana, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imani cewa Kavanaugh yana iya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake magana, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka faɗi haka game da Ford.
A cewar Flake, FBI ta fara binciken zargin da Ford da kuma akalla wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, suka yi, kamar yadda The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi lalata da ita lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa wani dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna al'aurarsa a wani biki.
Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web ya shirya sabon yanar gizo don ya yi wa Google da Facebook kara
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya fara farawa wanda zai kasance gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da almara na fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda aka gina akan dandamali na tushen buɗewa na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara inda za a adana bayanai da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar samun bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa niyyarsa a bayan Inrupt ita ce mamayar duniya.
"Muna bukatar mu yi hakan yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Dapp yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar yin amfani da nasu kantin sayar da bayanan kan layi ko POD.
Zai iya haɗa jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan yi, kalandarku, laburaren kiɗa da sauran kayan aikin mutum da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda, kuma suna yin hakan a kai a kai.
Abin da ke da banbanci game da "shafin yanar gizon sirri" shi ne cewa yana dogara ne akan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
Kamfanin ya kira shi " 'yanci na mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, shine kawo albarkatu, sarrafa ƙwarewa da kuma mallakar kansu don yin wannan ƙarfin ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikata masu aiki a matsayin masu ci gaba a kan aikin da kuma al'umma na masu aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba tare da kayan aikin da aka samo akan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook ko Google kan ko su kawo sauyi gaba daya, inda za a juya tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya cikin dare.
Ba mu nemi izini a nan.
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium, wanda aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa aikin Inrupt shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci a cikin tsarin halittu wanda ke da daraja don kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo a kan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza hanyar Intanet ta hanyar kafa Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da yake ya kafa Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai kafa da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Cibiyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina matukar fatan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Farfesa na yakin duniya na farko tare da giciye na Victoria
Shugaban Ikilisiyar Ingila wanda ya taba samun lambar yabo ta Victoria a lokacin yakin duniya na farko ya yi bikin cika shekaru 100 a garinsu.
Lt Col The Reverend Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a lokacin da aka kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma sai aka kawo shi ga wani maharbi har kwana hudu, kuma bai taba ganin cewa ya sami damar yin hakan ba.
An bayyana wani dutse na tunawa da shi tare da jikoki biyu a wani fareti a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "wani abu ne mai ban mamaki" cewa an bayyana dutse daidai shekaru 100 bayan aikin da ya yi, wanda ya ba shi lambar yabo.
A cewar London Gazette, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci bataliyarsa a kan Canal de Saint-Quentin a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 ta hanyar hazo mai zurfi da kuma kai hari a filin da kuma bindigogi.
Daga bisani ya gudu zuwa layin wuta kuma ya sake jagorantar battalion kafin ya dauki makami daya da hannu daya kuma ya kori uku daga cikin sojojin.
An kama Lt. Col. Vann ne a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918 daga wani dan jarida na Jamus - kawai wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ba zai iya yin adalci da ayyukan kakansa ba amma abin takaici ne.
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma ba da wata laure bayan bikin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin girmamawa sosai kasancewar yana cikin jerin gwanon kuma ya ce ƙarfin hali na gwarzo na gaskiya yana nunawa ta hanyar goyon bayan mutane da yawa.
MMA magoya zauna dukan dare don duba Bellator 206 kuma samu Peppa Pig maimakon
Ka yi tunanin wannan: Ka yi barci dukan dare kana kallon Bellator 206 mai cike da ƙwari, sai kawai ka ga cewa babban gidan ya ƙi ya ba ka ƙwai.
An shirya wasanni 13 daga San Jose, ciki har da shida a kan babban taswira kuma an nuna su a Channel 5 a duk dare a cikin United Kingdom.
Da karfe 6 na safe, lokacin da Gerard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin karawa, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka canza rahoto zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu ba su damu ba, sun kasance a faɗake har zuwa safiya don yin yaki.
Wani mai goyon baya ya bayyana sauyawa zuwa zane-zane na yara a Twitter a matsayin "wani irin hauka ne".
"Gwamnati ta ba da umarnin cewa a karfe 6 na safe abun ciki bai dace ba, don haka dole ne su canza zuwa shirin yara", in ji David Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban Bellator na kasuwanci da sadarwa, lokacin da yake jawabi a watsa shirye-shiryen.
""Peppa da alade", ya yi. "
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator Scott Coker ya ce suna son sake duba jadawalin su don hada masu kallo daga Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina ganin idan na yi tunani game da sake kunnawa, ina ganin za mu iya yin hakan", in ji Coker.
"Amma shi ne 6 da safe Lahadi da kuma ba mu iya inganta wannan har sai Lahadi mu lokaci, Litinin su lokaci.
Amma muna aiki a kai.
Na yi imani, lokacin da aka juya shi, an aika da saƙonni da yawa a can, kuma ba su da abokantaka.
Mun yi ƙoƙarin gyara shi, mun yi tunanin cewa wata matsala ce ta fasaha.
Amma babu, matsala ce ta shari'a.
Na tabbatar muku, wannan ba zai sake faruwa ba.
Mun rage yawan gwagwarmaya zuwa 5 maimakon 6 kamar yadda muke yi kullum kuma mun yi kokarin samar da karin magoya baya, amma mun kasa.
Wannan abin takaici ne".
Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji "ƙananan" game da jima'i
Mai wasan motsa jiki na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce an tashe shi da jin cewa ya fi kowa daraja saboda jima'i  amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don yin nasara.
Dan shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "ba kowa bane kamar ni".
A wata hira da aka yi da Radio 4 Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin maza don ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce zama iyaye ya sa ya kasa damuwa da lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon na tsawon lokaci, Kirsty Young, ya ɗauki hutu na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
A lokacin da ta fito a matsayin mai fita daga cikin shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce yana jin cewa yana girma "ba shi da daraja" fiye da kowa saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba a cikin zamantakewa don son yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "Har zuwa yau, jin cewa ba mu da daraja da kuma bambanci, su ne kawai abubuwan da suka ba mu ƙarfin jimrewa da kuma yin nasara".
Ya so ya tabbatar da cewa shi "mai daraja ne", in ji shi, don kada ya sa kowa ya yi baƙin ciki idan suka gano sha'awar jima'i a ƙarshe.
Gwarzon zinare na Olympics sau biyu yana daya daga cikin shahararrun masu goyon bayan LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da wasansa a wasannin Commonwealth a Ostiraliya a wannan shekara don yin kira ga karin kasashe su dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi wannan magana ne domin yana jin farin ciki, yana iya zama a buɗe kuma ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Gwarzon zakaran duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi mamakin yadda ya ƙaunaci wani mutum - mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya san shi a 2013 - "ya ba ni mamaki".
Daley ya auri Oscar wanda ya girmi shi da shekaru 20 a bara, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan kana da wannan shekarun, ka yi haka" - ya halarci gasar Olympics ta farko yana dan shekara daya kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu bayan shekaru uku da ciwon kansa - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wanda ya kai shekarunsa ya yi tsalle a tsaunuka da zurfin da ya kai.
Ma'auratan sun zama iyayen wani saurayi mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley a watan Yuni kuma Daley ya ce "duk hangen nesan" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da ya kasance game da 'Ina buƙatar lashe zinare,'" in ji shi.
"Ka san, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Robbie ne zinariyar Olympics".
Mahaifinsa yana da suna kamar mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambayi shi shine ko sun riga sun sami tikiti zuwa London 2012  saboda yana so ya zauna a jere na farko.
Ya ce, 'Ban ce masa, 'Kada ka zauna a gaban gado ba,' "in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na yarda cewa ba shi da ganuwa", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkin rayuwata duka - yin iyo a gaban taron jama'a a cikin gida a gasar Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Wannan ya kuma ba da shawarar zabar waƙar sa ta farko  Pride of Heather Small  wanda ya buga a bango yayin da yake shirya don wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu yana haifar da ƙanshi a cikin shi.
Desert Island Discs yana zuwa a ranar Lahadi a 11:15 BST akan BBC Radio 4.
Mickelson ya yi rashin lafiya a gasar cin kofin Ryder a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson ya kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi yayin da yake buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma dole ne ya dawo cikin siffar sa don kauce wa rashin jin daɗin wasan.
Mickelson, wanda ke buga wasa a karo na 12 a gasar da ake yi duk shekara biyu, ya yi wa kyaftin Jim Furyk kwallo hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda ya yi sau da yawa ga Amurka, mai cin nasara sau biyar ya yi amfani da ranarsa don yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma aiki a kan wasan, yana fatan ya inganta abin da yake shirin.
Ba ma a lokacin da ya fi tsayi a cikin aikinsa ba ne ya kasance mafi kyawun direba, kuma saboda haka dan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shi da kyakkyawan tsari don ƙarancin filin wasa na Le Golf National, inda dogon tsawo ya saba da azabtar da harbi.
Kuma idan wasannin da kansu ba su da ban tsoro, Mickelson zai fuskanci zakaran Birtaniya Open Francesco Molinari a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, wanda zai hada kai da mai farawa Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa sun fara wasa da maki hudu a raga guda 12 da suka fara, to wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai matukar muhimmanci.
Furyk ta bayyana wa mijinta asirin, ba haka ba ne zai iya faɗi wani abu dabam.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayinsa na yau sosai, ya rungume ni a baya, ya rungume ni kuma ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe".
"Yana da kwarin gwiwa.
Yana cikin jerin sunayen da suka fi dacewa kuma ya yi aiki sosai a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin cewa zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunani game da shi, amma wannan shine yadda ya yi aiki kuma yadda muka yi tunanin dole ne mu yi.
Yana son ya fita waje kamar kowa".
Mickelson ya karya rikodin Nick Faldo na mafi yawan wasannin Ryder Cup a ranar Lahadi.
Zai iya wakiltar ƙarshen aikin Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa kaiwa ga manyan abubuwan da ya samu ba.
Mickelson ya yi nasara 18, ya rasa wasanni 20 da rabi bakwai, amma Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya kawo fa'idodi da ba za a iya ganewa ba ga tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana son yin dariya game da wasu kuma mutum ne mai ban mamaki wanda ake so a cikin ɗakin aiki", in ji shi.
"Ina tsammanin matasa 'yan wasa suna jin daɗin tafiya tare da shi, kuma wannan makon ma ya kasance mai ban sha'awa.
Yana da fiye da kawai wasanni".
Turai kyaftin Thomas Bjorn sani sani cewa babban ci gaba iya bace da sauri
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya san cewa babban ci gaba a wasan karshe na Ryder Cup zai iya zama mummunan magana.
Dan wasan ya fara wasa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama, inda tawagar da ke karkashin jagorancin Seve Ballesteros ta ci gaba da samun maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma ta ci gaba da tsalle-tsalle a 141⁄2:131⁄2.
"Kullum kuna tuna cewa muna da babban matsayi a Valderrama; muna da babban matsayi a Brookline inda muka rasa, kuma a Valderrama inda muka ci nasara, amma kuma kusa", in ji Bjorn, yana mai cewa bayan ya ga ajin 2018 sun ci duka Jumma'a da jiya da 5-3 don su jagoranci Le Golf National da 10-6.
Don haka tarihi zai nuna mana da kowa a cikin tawagar cewa wannan ba ta ƙare ba tukuna.
Ku tafi da shi gobe.
Ku fita can ku yi kome daidai.
Wannan ba shi da shi har sai kun ga dots a kan brim.
Muna da wata manufa, kuma ita ce mu yi kokarin lashe wannan kofin, kuma wannan shine abin da ya kamata mu ci gaba da mayar da hankali a kai.
Na ce a koyaushe, ina mai da hankali ne ga 'yan wasan 12 da ke gefenmu, amma mun san abin da ke gefenmu - 'yan wasan da suka fi kyau a duniya".
Da yake jin daɗin ganin yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi nasara a kan wani filin golf mai wuya, Bjorn ya kara da cewa: "Ba zan taɓa yin watsi da kaina ba.
Gobe za mu sami wata dabba a gabanmu.
Gobe, za a yi amfani da wasu abubuwa, kuma wannan shine takalma na biyu.
Yana da kyau mutum ya fita waje tare da abokin tarayya idan abubuwa suna tafiya daidai, amma idan mutum ya fita waje shi kadai, sai a gwada shi da jini kamar mai wasan golf.
Wannan shine sakon da ya kamata ku gaya wa 'yan wasan: Ku kasance mafi kyau gobe.
Amma yanzu ka bar abokin aikinka ya tafi, ya kawo kayansa. "
A bambanci da Bjorn, abokin hamayyarsa, Jim Furyk, yana son 'yan wasan su yi nasara a kan kansu fiye da yadda suka yi a matsayin abokan tarayya, banda Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ɗauki maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya san bangarorin biyu na manyan juyin juya halin, saboda ya kasance wani ɓangare na ƙungiyar da ta yi nasara a Brooklyn kafin ta yi watsi da matsayin da ta rasa, saboda Turai ta buga "Miracle of Medina".
"Na tuna da kowane kalma na wannan", in ji shi a cikin amsar tambayar lokacin da Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin a 1999, ya tara 'yan wasansa kafin ranar ƙarshe.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna so ku fara da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brooklyn, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madinah.
Idan pendulum ya yi tafiya a cikin wani shugabanci, yana sanya matsin lamba a kan matsakaici.
Mun kafa ƙa'ida da za mu bi, kuma mun sa mutanen su yi ta yin sihiri kamar yadda muke tsammani za mu yi gobe. "
An ba Thomas aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar ƙetare kuma yana fuskantar Rory McIlroy a cikin babban wasan, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter, sauran Turai a ɗayan rabin saitin.
"Na zabi wannan jerin saboda ina tsammanin ya rufe komai", in ji Bjorn game da zaɓin sa na ɗaya.
A sabon jirgin ruwan yaki na Jamus sake koma bayan hanne
An ba da umarnin sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a kammala shi ba a cikin shekara mai zuwa, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na gida, saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar kuɗi.
An sake wajabta odar "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan jirgin ruwa na Baden Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar "Die Zeit", wanda ya ambaci wani mai magana da yawun soja.
An shirya jirgi zai shiga Sojojin Ruwa a 2014, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da bayarwa sun sa makomar wannan babban shiri ta yi tsalle.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Württemberg, wanda rundunar sojan ruwa ta umarci a shekarar 2007, an tsara su ne don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Suna da makamai masu linzami, da makamai masu linzami da na jirgin sama, da kuma fasahar ɓoyewa kamar rage radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman ayyuka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa  ya kamata ya yiwu cewa sabbin jiragen ruwa ba su isa tashar jirgin ruwa ba har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Amma jinkirin da ake samu na ci gaba da haifar da sabbin jiragen yakin  wadanda za su tabbatar wa Jamus da karfinta a kasashen ketare  cewa sun riga sun tsufa kafin su shiga aiki, "Zeit" ya lura.
Jirgin ruwan F125 da ya faru da rashin alheri ya zama sanannen sanarwa a bara lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin ruwa kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da sojojin suka sake tura jirgin ruwa zuwa wani jirgin ruwa bayan an ba da shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka sake dawowa ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu "kasawa na software da kayan aiki" da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a cikin aikin yaki.
