An yi wa dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers Christion Abercrombie tiyata bayan da ya ji rauni a kan kansa a wasan da aka yi da Vanderbilt Commodores a ranar Asabar, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Tennessee.
