"Ya zo kan iyakar kuma ya fadi a can", in ji Reed.
Masu horarwa da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ba Abercrombie iskar oxygen a gefen gefen kuma suka sanya shi a kan giya kuma suka kawo shi zuwa ga Hannun don ƙarin kimantawa.
Wani jami'in jihar Tennessee ya shaida wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee cewa Abercrombie ya bar dakin aiki na Vanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris ya kara da cewa "babu wani bayani game da yanayin / girman laifin" kuma jihar Tennessee na kokarin gano lokacin da laifin ya faru.
Wannan shi ne Abercrombie, dan wasa na biyu a kwalejin, a farkon kakar wasa a Jihar Tennessee bayan ya koma daga Illinois.
