Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa jihar Palu ta Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji majiyoyin, tare da tsammanin adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace, jami'an tsaro ba su sami damar samun bayanai daga Donggala Regency, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana gab da cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afku.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) daga gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Harkokin kiwo na kiwo yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da guguwar tsunami a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami a Donggalami ya kashe mutane 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yanayin girgizar kasa kuma ana yawan fuskantar girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A jerin karfi girgizar asa buga yammacin Coast na Sumatra a karshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: A 6.8 ƙarfin ya buga kudancin Java, tsibirin mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibiran Menawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata garuruwa da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haifar da barna da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami.
Babu wata tsunami da aka yi a lokacin, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 ta hanyar faduwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Indonesiya Lombok, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta tsare dubban masu yawon bude ido a tsibirin na dan lokaci.
